   "source": [
    "# Sandbox\n",
    "\n",
    "This is a sandbox"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# base\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import networkx as nx\n",
    "from pandas_plink import read_plink\n",
    "from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer\n",
    "import pkg_resources\n",
    "\n",
    "# viz\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import cartopy.crs as ccrs\n",
    "\n",
    "# feems\n",
    "from feems.utils import prepare_graph_inputs\n",
    "from feems import SpatialGraph, Viz"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Mapping files: 100%|██████████| 3/3 [00:00<00:00, 47.13it/s]\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# path to example data\n",
    "data_path = pkg_resources.resource_filename(\"feems\", \"data/\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# read the genotype data and mean impute missing data\n",
    "(bim, fam, G) = read_plink(\"{}/wolvesadmix\".format(data_path))\n",
    "imp = SimpleImputer(missing_values=np.nan, strategy=\"mean\")\n",
    "genotypes = imp.fit_transform((np.array(G)).T)\n",
    "    \n",
    "# setup graph\n",
    "coord = np.loadtxt(\"{}/wolvesadmix.coord\".format(data_path))\n",
    "outer = np.loadtxt(\"{}/wolvesadmix.outer\".format(data_path))\n",
    "grid_path = \"{}/grid_250.shp\".format(data_path)\n",
    "outer, edges, grid, ipmap = prepare_graph_inputs(coord=coord,\n",
    "                                                 ggrid=grid_path,\n",
    "                                                 translated=True,\n",
    "                                                 buffer=0,\n",
    "                                                 outer=outer)\n",
    "sp_graph = SpatialGraph(genotypes, coord, grid, edges)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Fit"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "constant-w/variance fit, converged in 130 iterations, train_loss=-175257.7594991\n",
      "lambda_l2=0.0000000, lambda=0.0010000, alpha=50.0000000, converged in 81 iterations, train_loss=-212563.2746100\n",
      "CPU times: user 4.04 s, sys: 66.8 ms, total: 4.11 s\n",
      "Wall time: 1.09 s\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "%%time\n",
    "sp_graph.fit_null_model()\n",
    "sp_graph.fit_quasi_newton(sp_graph.w0, 0, .001, 50)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Viz"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1800x1200 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "projection = ccrs.EquidistantConic(central_longitude=-108.842926, central_latitude=66.037547)\n",
    "fig = plt.figure(dpi=300)\n",
    "ax = fig.add_subplot(1, 1, 1, projection=projection)  \n",
    "\n",
    "# setup viz and attributes\n",
    "v = Viz(ax, sp_graph, projection=projection)\n",
    "v.edge_width = .5\n",
    "v.edge_alpha = 1\n",
    "v.edge_zorder = 100\n",
    "v.sample_pt_color = \"black\"\n",
    "v.sample_pt_size = 20\n",
    "v.sample_pt_alpha = 1.0\n",
    "v.sample_pt_jitter_std = 0.2\n",
    "v.obs_node_size = 7.5\n",
    "v.obs_node_textsize = 5\n",
    "v.obs_node_alpha = 1.0\n",
    "v.cbar_font_size = 10\n",
    "v.cbar_orientation = \"horizontal\"\n",
    "v.ell_lw = .1\n",
    "v.ell_abs_max = .5\n",
    "v.ell_edgecolor = \"black\"\n",
    "v.target_dist_pt_size = 50\n",
    "v.target_dist_pt_linewidth = .5\n",
    "v.target_dist_pt_alpha = 1.0\n",
    "v.target_dist_pt_zorder = 2\n",
    "v.draw_map()\n",
    "v.draw_edges(use_weights=True)\n",
    "v.draw_obs_nodes(use_ids=False) \n",
    "v.draw_edge_colorbar()"
   ]
